name: TYR Lambent Blade Splice Jammer Swimsuit - Men's
description: A streamlined suit that won’t interfere with your hydrodynamics. Whether you’re training for your first triathlon, next race, or just getting a few laps in, the Blade Splice jammer has a smooth fit to cut through the water.Durafast Elite™ polyester is chlorine and fade-resistant.Fabric provides UPF 50+ sun protection.Full lining has an antimicrobial treatment.Compression fit and drawcord waist.
